he frontend (HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery). '),(323,244,'_codelab__description','Web design is everything you see on a website. Well start the web design process with wireframes and high-fidelity mockups in Sketch. Using InVision, well create an interactive mockup for clients to see and leave comments on the web design. After revising the web design to your liking, well move to the frontend (HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery). '),(324,244,'_codelab_card_title','Web Dev'),(325,244,'_codelab_card_url','4'),(326,239,'_codelab__description','Web design is everything you see on a website. Well start the web design process with wireframes and high-fidelity mockups in Sketch. Using InVision, well create an interactive mockup for clients to see and leave comments on the web design. After revising the web design to your liking, well move to the frontend (HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery). '),(327,239,'_codelab_card_title','Web Apps'),(328,239,'_codelab_card_url','4'),(329,245,'_codelab_description','User interface / user experience designs are how we always start any web app or web design projects. This allows us to quickly wireframe out web designs / ui designs so that we can get approval from clients on layout. After, we move from wireframe to low fidelity then high fidelity mockups. At this stage, the web app or web design is finalized and prototyped with tools such as InVision.'),(330,244,'_codelab_description','Software development in 2018 is much more modular than ever. There are so many frameworks &amp; platforms that finding the right stack can be intimidating at times. Throughout our experiences, we found javascript frontend frameworks like React &amp; AngularJS to be a powerful toolset. Our backend ranges from Node.js, Python, to Laravel, all of which are useful depending on the project scope. Our goal is to find the perfect technology for your custom projects.\r\n'),(331,239,'_codelab_description','Web design is everything you see on a website. Well start the web design process with wireframes and high-fidelity mockups in Sketch. Using InVision, well create an interactive mockup for clients to see and leave comments on the web design. After revising the designs to your liking, well move to the frontend (HTML, CSS, JS, Jquery). Any type of animation would be created in Javascript/jQuery after code revisions take place.'),(332,254,'inline_featured_image','0'),(333,254,'_edit_last','1'),(334,254,'_edit_lock','1517721637:1'),(335,254,'_thumbnail_id','243'),(336,255,'inline_featured_image','0'),(337,255,'inline_featured_image','0'),(338,255,'_edit_last','1'),(339,255,'_edit_lock','1517721647:1'),(340,255,'_thumbnail_id','243'),(344,256,'inline_featured_image','0'),(345,256,'inline_featured_image','0'),(346,256,'inline_featured_image','0'),(347,256,'_edit_last','1'),(348,256,'_edit_lock','1517721997:1'),(349,256,'_thumbnail_id','243'),(352,1,'_wp_trash_meta_status','publish'),(353,1,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1517722149'),(354,1,'_wp_desired_post_slug','hello-world'),(355,1,'inline_featured_image','0'),(356,1,'_wp_trash_meta_comments_status','a:1:{i:1;s:1:\"1\";}'),(357,258,'inline_featured_image','0'),(358,258,'_edit_last','1'),(359,258,'_edit_lock','1518602608:1'),(362,258,'_thumbnail_id','315'),(365,260,'inline_featured_image','0'),(366,260,'inline_featured_image','0'),(367,260,'_edit_last','1'),(368,260,'_edit_lock','1518405932:1'),(371,260,'_thumbnail_id','315'),(383,262,'inline_featured_image','0'),(384,262,'inline_featured_image','0'),(385,262,'inline_featured_image','0'),(386,262,'_thumbnail_id','315'),(389,262,'_dp_original','260'),(390,262,'_edit_lock','1518405906:1'),(391,262,'_edit_last','1'),(394,262,'_wp_old_slug','7-marketing-tools-great-for-entrepreneurs-all-free-2'),(395,264,'_wp_attached_file','2018/02/codelab.svg'),(396,265,'_wp_trash_meta_status','publish'),(397,265,'_wp_trash_meta_time','1517724540'),(398,264,'_edit_lock','1517724553:1'),(399,266,'_wp_attached_file','2018/02/300x100.png'),(400,266,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";