 italic;n  font-weight: 100;n}nn#item {n  padding-left:10px;n  font-size: 1.2em;n  font-weight: 500;n}nn.box {n    margin: 30px auto;n    font-weight: 600;n    display: block;n    padding: 30px;n  tbackground-color: #F5F5F5;n    border-radius: 10px;n    -webkit-transition: 0.2s;n    transition: 0.2s;n}n.box:hover {n  background-color: #2e3638;ntcolor:white;n  -webkit-transition: 0.2s;n    transition: 0.2s;n}nn.notify-dot {n  color: #EA0000;n  font-size: 2em;n}\",\"custom_js\":\"//n// No need to add script tagsn// here; simply get startedn// by writing JavaScript!n// Remember to save yourn// changes to see them :)n//nn\",\"custom_js_mini\":\"\",\"responsive_text\":[]}'),(876,3336,'_x_entry_body_css_class',''),(877,3336,'_x_entry_alternate_index_title',''),(878,3336,'_x_entry_bg_image_full',''),(879,3336,'_x_entry_bg_image_full_fade','750'),(880,3336,'_x_entry_bg_image_full_duration','7500'),(881,3336,'_x_post_layout',''),(882,3336,'_cornerstone_data','[{\"_type\":\"section\",\"title\":\"Section 1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"row\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h2>What Is Inbound Marketing?</h2>nn<strong>Inbound marketing</strong> involves customers or prospects coming to you. This can be from them visiting your website, contacting you for services, calling in, etc.nnThis is the often more sought after form of marketing because nnInstead of having salesperson calling clients, the clients are the ones reaching out to the business. And by what mysterious voodoo magic can this be achieved you might ask. The answer is through <strong>content marketing</strong>.nnIn other words, inbound marketing is just a big umbrella term for any type of marketing that brings the attention of an audience. In contrast to outbound marketing, where the business actively seeks out to the audience, inbound marketing is the other way around.\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 2\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"The field of digital marketing hasu00a0witnessed a huge growth as social media became ubiquitous in our modern age. With so many marketing strategies and terminologies, it can be confusing sometimes to even people within the industry. Inbounding marketing and content marketing are two of those terms that are used interchangeably, despite minute nuances.\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 3\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h2>What Is Contentu00a0Marketing?</h2>nnContent marketing is one of those strategies businesses employ to gain the attention of potential customers. By producing relevant and enticing content, users will subscribe to newsletter and keep updated with future updates. Not only is this strategy more authentic then cold calling clients, it provides greater long term value for your customer.\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 4\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h2>Other Types Inbound Marketing</h2>nnIn other words, content marketing is a subset of inbound marketing. There are other forms of inbound marketing, as content marketing is not the only strategy.nn<h3>Social Media</h3>nnSocial media is another form on inbound marketing. By deciding whatu00a0information to share, you choose to connect with a certain type of audience. You can shape your online image by carefully showing interest in certain subjects. You may say that isn\'t genuine or authentic, but that is the gist of social media. You decide what to share to the world to show that you are cool.nn<h3>SEO</h3>nnSEO is very similar to content marketing. Both you are sharing useful content to draw the users in. SEO is strictly just the text on your web page, and not any additional material you may provide on your site. You may have an e-book or tutorials on a subject, but that wouldn\'t be considered SEO because a search engine can\'t index the information contained within a video, or a PDF.nn<h3>PPC</h3>nnThere has been some debate about whetheru00a0PPC is inbound or outbound marketing. Since traditional advertising is considered outbound marketing, some people are saying PPC is advertising as well, and should be considered outbound. However, some people argue that since PPC links are related to the keywords you type in, the user was already actively looking for the information. In either case, PPC is another method you can draw users into your site.n\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}]}]'),(883,3336,'_cornerstone_excerpt','Inbound marketing involves customers or prospects coming to you. This can be from them visiting your website, contacting you for services, calling in, etc. This is the often more sought after form of marketing because'),(884,3336,'_cornerstone_version','2.0.4'),(885,3336,'_yst_is_cornerstone',''),(886,3336,'_x_quote_quote',''),(887,3336,'_x_quote_cite',''),(888,3336,'_x_link_url',''),(889,3336,'_x_video_aspect_ratio','16:9'),(890,3336,'_x_video_m4v',''),(891,3336,'_x_video_ogv',''),(892,3336,'_x_video_embed',''),(893,3336,'_x_audio_mp3',''),(894,3336,'_x_audio_ogg',''),(895,3336,'_x_audio_embed',''),(896,3336,'the_grid_item_custom_link_target','_self'),(897,3336,'the_grid_item_col','1'),(898,3336,'the_grid_item_row','1'),(899,3336,'the_grid_item_content_color','dark'),(900,3336,'the_grid_item_overlay_color','light'),(901,3336,'the_grid_item_video_ratio','4:3'),(902,3336,'the_grid_item_youtube_ratio','4:3'),(903,3336,'the_grid_item_vimeo_ratio','4:3'),(904,3336,'the_grid_item_wistia_ratio','4:3'),(905,3336,'_yoast_wpseo_content_score','30'),(906,3413,'inline_featured_image','0'),(907,3413,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(908,3413,'_edit_last','2'),(909,3413,'slide_template','default'),(910,3413,'_thumbnail_id','3419'),(911,3413,'ut_activate_csection','global'),(912,3413,'ut_csection_background_image','a:5:{s:17:\"background-repeat\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"background-attachment\";s:0:\"\";s:19:\"background-position\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"background-size\";s:0:\"\";s:16:\"background-image\";s:0:\"\";}'),(913,3413,'ut_csection_overlay','on'),(914,3413,'ut_csection_overlay_opacity','0.8'),(915,3413,'ut_sh