oday.nnFor some reason you didn\'t buy anything, maybe you had to take a call, your house was on fire, it can be anything. You left the shop.nnThat coffee shop lost a potential customer. <strong>Until now.</strong>nnAs you\'re on your way home, all the billboards you pass by, actually have your local coffee shop advertising on them.\"},{\"_type\":\"line\",\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 2\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"image\",\"elements\":[],\"src\":\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Facebook-Remarketing-for-Local-Businesses-min-1.jpg\",\"alt\":\"Facebook Marketing for Local Businesses\",\"image_style\":\"rounded\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 3\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"Not only are you seeing their ads but you\'re seeing offers that are <strong>relevant and enticing to you</strong> - the potential customer.nn<strong></strong>nn<span class=\"popout\">Now that business has more plenty of opportunities to bring you back in as a customer. It\'s a game-changer.</a></span> nBasically, Facebook can do just this, except for online advertising (and even offline to some degree).\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}],\"padding\":[\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]},{\"_type\":\"section\",\"title\":\"Facebook Remarketing\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"Copy of New Item 2\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h2 id=\"Remarketing\">What is Facebook Remarketing?</h2></strong><strong>Facebook Remarketing refers to the strategy of displaying ads, offers, and discounts, to people that have visited your website </strong>(making them potential customers),<strong> while they\'re browsing Facebook</strong>.nnYou can even display ads to people who have purchased from you in the past. Display up-sells, cross-sells, etc and bring them back to your site every time.nnAnyone that visit\'s your website can automatically be put into what\'s called a <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/341425252616329\"><strong>Facebook Custom Audience</strong></a> (and then into a Remarketing List).nn<span class=\"box\"><span id=\"item\"><a href=\"https://emailoctopus.com/\">What is a Facebook Custom Audience?</a></span>n\"A Custom Audience from a customer list is a type of audience you can create made up of your existing customers. You can target ads to the audience you\'ve created on Facebook, Instagram, and Audience Network.\"</span> - <i>Source: Facebook Help Center</i>\"},{\"_type\":\"line\",\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}],\"padding\":[\"0px\",\"0px\",\"45px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]},{\"_type\":\"row\",\"title\":\"New Item 3\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h3 id=\"Importance\">Why is this so important?</h3>nnNow here\'s the fun part.nn<strong>Anytime someone visits your website, they are anonymously saved to your custom audience.</strong>nn<strong>Then, the next time they are on Facebook, they are going to see YOUR ADS in their news feed or side bar.</strong>nnMost people are on Facebook at some point these days, including your target customer, roughly <strong>2 billion people/month </strong> log on.nnSo these people seeing your ads are going to be <strong>very likely to purchase or sign up</strong> because they\'ve already been to your website and are most likely interested in what you have to offer.\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}],\"padding\":[\"55px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]},{\"_type\":\"section\",\"title\":\"How to Get Started\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"row\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h4 id=\"GetStarted\">How to Get Started</h4>nIn order to build a custom audience from people who have purchased from you or <strong>visited your website</strong> (which are some of the best kind of people by the way - it makes sense, they\'ve raised their hand and shown an interest in what you have to offer as a business), you need install a <strong>Facebook Pixel</strong>.nn<i>*This part you might need to be a little technically inclined for or send this guide to someone who is.</i>nn<span class=\"popout\">How to Install your Facebook Pixel (Free Guide)n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.facebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></span> nn<i>The page will look something like this:</i>\"},{\"_type\":\"image\",\"elements\":[],\"alt\":\"Facebook Pixel Guide Tutorial\",\"src\":\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Facebook-Pixel-Guide-min.jpg\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}],\"padding\":[\"0px\",\"0px\",\"45px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]},{\"_type\":\"section\",\"title\":\"How to Create the Facebook Audience\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"row\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h5  id=\"Audience\">How to Create the Audience</h5>n<span class=\"popout\">Visit your Facebook Ads Managern<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ads/manager/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.fac\nebook.com/business/help/952192354843755</a></span>nnOnce you\'re in your <strong>Facebook Ads Manager</strong>, go ahead and click on the <img src=\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Hamburger.jpg\"> and follow the instructions in the images below.\"},{\"_type\":\"image\",\"elements\":[],\"src\":\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Steps-1-and-2-min.png\"},{\"_type\":\"image\",\"elements\":[],\"src\":\"https://codelabstudios.dev/app/uploads/2017/08/Facebook-Custom-Audience-Types.jpg\",\"image_style\":\"rounded\"},{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"And that\'s basically it for the basics on setting up a custom audience for remarketing. \"},{\"_type\":\"line\",\"elements\":[]}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}],\"padding\":[\"20px\",\"0px\",\"45px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]},{\"_type\":\"section\",\"title\":\"Conclusion\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"row\",\"_column_layout\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"column\",\"_active\":true,\"size\":\"1/1\",\"elements\":[{\"_type\":\"text\",\"elements\":[],\"content\":\"<h6 id=\"Conclusion\">Conclusion</h6>nThis is just the beginner\'s guide on <strong>what is Facebook Remarketing & How to get Started</strong>. It gets complicated from here when it comes down to targeting the audience, creating ads, A/B testing campaigns, optimizing for conversions, getting people to actually buy from you, and scaling up. If you\'re not careful, you can waste money.nnn<span class=\"popout\">If Facebook Advertising sounds like something you\'d want to look into, give us a call and get some free advice.</span>nn<a href=\"tel:844-260-5003\" class=\"call\" target=\"_blank\">(844) 260-5003</a></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Or via&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codelabstudios.dev/services/#contact\" class=\"call\" target=\"_blank\">Contact Form</a>\",\"text_align\":\"c\"}]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]},{\"_type\":\"column\",\"size\":\"1/1\",\"_active\":false,\"elements\":[]}]}],\"padding\":[\"0px\",\"0px\",\"45px\",\"0px\",\"unlinked\"]}]'),(1024,4191,'_cornerstone_excerpt','So if you&#8217;re interested in advertising on Facebook in 2017, you should first know about Facebook Remarketing, Why it&#8217;s amazing, and how to utilize it. I&#8217;ll explain all of this for you below.'),(1025,4191,'_cornerstone_version','2.0.6'),(1026,4191,'_oembed_e60230841a94473742228645a822361b','{{unknown}}'),(1027,4191,'_wp_old_slug','free-guide-install-retarget-with-facebook-pixel'),(1028,4191,'_yoast_wpseo_primary_category','41'),(1029,4191,'_x_quote_quote',''),(1030,4191,'_x_quote_cite',''),(1031,4191,'_x_link_url',''),(1032,4191,'_x_video_aspect_ratio','16:9'),(1033,4191,'_x_video_m4v',''),(1034,4191,'_x_video_ogv',''),(1035,4191,'_x_video_embed',''),(1036,4191,'_x_audio_mp3',''),(1037,4191,'_x_audio_ogg',''),(1038,4191,'_x_audio_embed',''),(1039,4191,'the_grid_item_custom_link_target','_self'),(1040,4191,'the_grid_item_col','1'),(1041,4191,'the_grid_item_row','1'),(1042,4191,'the_grid_item_content_color','dark'),(1043,4191,'the_grid_item_overlay_color','light'),(1044,4191,'the_grid_item_video_ratio','4:3'),(1045,4191,'the_grid_item_youtube_ratio','4:3'),(1046,4191,'the_grid_item_vimeo_ratio','4:3'),(1047,4191,'the_grid_item_wistia_ratio','4:3'),(1048,4191,'_yoast_wpseo_opengraph-title','What is Facebook Remarketing?'),(1049,4191,'_yoast_wpseo_title','What is Facebook Remarketing and is it Important in 2017?'),(1050,4191,'_yoast_wpseo_metadesc','This is a beginner\'s guide to teach you the basics of Facebook Remarketing, Facebook Custom Audiences, installing the Facebook Pixel, and more!'),(1051,4191,'_yoast_wpse